# Klyuchi, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Klyuchi () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ivolginsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. As of 2010, the population was 103. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Klyuchi is located 10&nbsp;km southwest of Ivolginsk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Ivolginsk is the nearest rural locality.
